text: Asked Old lady on counter on. Friday 4:20pm that where is tongue cleaner she said sold out we don’t have . Don’t know why keeping staff who don’t want to sell stuff. So after searching for 20 minutes finally found it . Not nice and not coming back .
They close the counter by 9:30pm but still it shows open till 10pm. Went to buy medicines as last resort and they say counter closed.

Completely oblivious of people standing in line waiting for payment. Only interested in serving the current customer in a difficult and long winded conversation. If my medication does not have my personal details stuck unto the box I would have just left.

This is at around 430pm.

Told the cashier, she said "no choice la." Thank you for that.

Go there if you have plenty of time to wait or when there is absolutely novody in the store.
I was looking for a single piece of face mask. The wonderful receptionist at the cashier offered me one FOC from her own supply. Such a kind and caring lady. Kudos to her!
Staffs there are generally friendly, knowledgeable and approachable. Many brands of supplements can be found there.
